---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  ogTitle="About Chill-Dogs | Curated Dog Lifestyle Products"
  description="Learn about Chill-Dogs — a simple, focused resource for cooling and relaxation products that help keep dogs comfortable."
>
  <section class="about container">
    <div class="prose">
      <h1>About Chill-Dogs</h1>
      <p>
        Welcome to Chill-Dogs — a simple, focused resource for dog owners who want practical products that provide comfort, safety and security to their dogs.
      </p>
      <p>
        We created Chill-Dogs to make it easier to find reliable cooling, calming and relaxation products without sorting through thousands of options online. We focus on three areas:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Cooling products for warm days</li>
        <li>Calming products for high-energy moments</li>
        <li>Relaxation products that provide everyday comfort and security</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>What We Cover</h2>
      <h3>Cooling</h3>
      <p>
        Hot weather can be tough on dogs. We highlight products designed to help them stay safe and comfortable, including:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Cooling mats and elevated beds</li>
        <li>Lightweight cooling vests and bandanas</li>
        <li>Water play options</li>
        <li>Freezable toys and treats</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Calming</h3>
      <p>
        Some situations are stressful for dogs. We curate products that many dog owners use during:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Thunderstorms</li>
        <li>Fireworks</li>
        <li>Bath time</li>
        <li>Travel</li>
        <li>Time alone at home</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        This may include:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Anxiety vests</li>
        <li>Compression wraps</li>
        <li>Relaxation-support chews</li>
        <li>Lickable mats</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Relaxing</h3>
      <p>
        All dogs deserve a place they can call their own. We select products that provide a sense of safety and security:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Crates</li>
        <li>Dog beds</li>
        <li>Blankets</li>
        <li>Plush toys</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 id="how-we-choose">How We Choose Products</h2>
      <p>
        We prioritize quality, durability, value, and positive customer reviews.
      </p>
      <p>
        Chill-Dogs is about helping you find the best products to keep your dog safe and comfortable at home and on the road.
      </p>
      <p>
        We use affiliate links to support the site. If you purchase through our links, we may earn a small commission at no additional cost to you. This does not affect which products we choose to feature.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    padding-top: var(--space-3xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
  }

  .about h1 {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }
</style>
